{"tid":1883364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑衣男突襲飛擲紅油彈 女保安走避不及半邊身染紅","createTime":"2020-02-17T01:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T01:41:21.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"51ea8458e16edde704926c5ff7cc3448d5393439","tid":1883364,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQoBqsC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQoBqsC.jpg&h=50173404&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0GDhUkX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0GDhUkX.jpg&h=e02c266b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港仔華富二邨商場保安櫃枱，凌晨2時許，一名穿黑色衫褲、架黑眼鏡、戴帽及口罩男子，手持一袋紅油衝向保安櫃枱，不發一言，向正返回櫃枱的姓凌女保安員飛擲紅油袋，其後隨即逃離現場，女保安右身衫褲大片染紅，警員接報到場展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n女保安員稱，在商場當保安逾一年，不清楚呈兇者目的，事發時剛添加開水準備返回櫃枱途中，遭男子掟紅油彈。女保安事後拒絶送院，更換衣服後繼續值班。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200217/LVUBBUBFHWUVNONUQSXUSEDJAI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200217%2FLVUBBUBFHWUVNONUQSXUSEDJAI%2F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=dcea520c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200217%2FLVUBBUBFHWUVNONUQSXUSEDJAI%2F&h=d8715da7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200217/LVUBBUBFHWUVNONUQSXUSEDJAI/</a>"},{"pid":"c203a0c9c3b63db7faa0c78089f9e586d15917b3","tid":1883364,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:41:21.000Z","msg":"立到油彈自動map咗去汽油彈揮手區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}